</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/f22276bc48d131dadc7e4dacbf38cee3ed05d536" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -0.838ex; width:9.644ex; height:2.843ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle P(A=
\cap B)}"></span> and substituting into the above expression for <span clas=
s=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-math=
ml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=3D"htt=
p://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyle P(A\vert B)}">
