iki/Sensitivity_and_specificity" title=3D"Sensitivity and specificity">spec=
ificity</a> of 91%, then the positive Bayes factor is <span class=3D"mwe-ma=
th-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline m=
we-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.=
org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyle \Lambda _{+}=3DP({\text{Tru=
