<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Bayes'_theorem_for_3_events=
"><span id=3D"Bayes.27_theorem_for_3_events"></span>Bayes' theorem for 3 ev=
ents</h3><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-brack=
et">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DBayes%2=
7_theorem&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D26" title=3D"Edit section: Bayes'=
 theorem for 3 events"><span>edit</span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-b=
racket">]</span></span></div>
<p>A version of Bayes' theorem for 3 events<sup id=3D"cite_ref-koller09_28-=
0" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bayes%27_th=
eorem#cite_note-koller09-28"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>27<span c=
lass=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup> results from the addition of a thi=
rd event <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span cla=
ss=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"=
><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaysty=
le C}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <mi>C</mi>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle C}</annotatio=
n>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/4fc55753007cd3c18576f7933f6f089196732029" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -0.338ex; width:1.766ex; height:2.176ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle C}"=
></span>, with <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><sp=
an class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: =
none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\disp=
laystyle P(C)&gt;0,}">
