 C)=3DP(B\cap A\cap C)=3DP(B\vert A\cap C)\,P(A\vert C)\,P(C)}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/a2a8c5b795d0388159a0924854246669649f6e0b" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
